{
  "texts": [
    "• Machine learning model/algorithm.",
    "The machine learning algorithm/model is also an essential aspect of our analysis as it provides the technical interpretation of the attack design under study.",
    "It is considered an influential factor in identifying the design and complexity of adversarial attacks.",
    "Also, it helps us to highlight the impact of attack type on individual machine learning algorithms.",
    "• Exploited vulnerability of machine learning algorithm."
  ]
}